snippet.title: Ming's Challenge for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

Game description:

Stop the shields and kill shooting ghosts and UFO's until the barrier at the bottom is completely destroyed.


What I think:

More like "Ming's Frustration" ... :\
